team1.name: Sentinels
team1.description: Sentinels is an American esports organization based in Los Angeles which fields teams in Fortnite, Hearthstone, Apex Legends and VALORANT.

player.bio: Shahzeeb "ShahZaM" Khan (born October 8, 1993) is an American professional VALORANT player who currently plays for Sentinels.
Jared "zombs" Gitlin (born October 2, 1998) is an American professional VALORANT player who currently plays for Sentinels.
Michael "dapr" Gulino (born January 1, 1999) is an American professional VALORANT player who currently plays for Sentinels.
Tyson "TenZ" Ngo (born May 5, 2001) is a Canadian professional VALORANT player who currently plays for Cloud9.
Hunter "SicK" Mims (born September 2, 1998) is an American professional VALORANT player who currently plays for Sentinels.
Domagoj "doma" Fancev (born July 29, 2003) is a Croatian player who currently plays for SUMN FC.
